      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh i just had the weirdest thing happen. like i was just sitting in my dorm and suddenly i got this massive headache that felt like a literal bolt of lightning hit my head. it was so intense i actually thought i was gonna pass out but it went away after a minute or two. now i just feel kinda foggy and weird. i've probably not drank enough water today since i've been studying for finals... do u think i'm just dehydrated or is something actually wrong?",
